data.name: TemplateDescription
desc: The implementation of a FilePicker service may support the usage of different templates.
The following constants define the currently specified templates.

items.name: FILEOPEN_SIMPLE
lines: A FileOpen dialog without any additional controls.

items.name: FILESAVE_SIMPLE
lines: A FileSave dialog without any additional controls.

items.name: FILESAVE_AUTOEXTENSION_PASSWORD
lines: A FileSave dialog with additional controls.

items.name: FILESAVE_AUTOEXTENSION_SELECTION
lines: A FileSave dialog with additional controls.

items.name: FILESAVE_AUTOEXTENSION_TEMPLATE
lines: A FileSave dialog with additional controls.

items.name: FILEOPEN_LINK_PREVIEW_IMAGE_TEMPLATE
lines: A FileOpen dialog with additional controls.

lines: A FileSave dialog with additional controls.
